posts.body:
>>6e0c1900-a558-49cb-bba2-fa29da04a331
This developed in a totally unexpected direction. Kudos.

There are tons of peers who are just lurking around. Are they scared they'll see something they don't want to? Or is everyone waiting for a moderator to come clean up? The only mod around is each individual user and her mute button.

On the other hand, isn't a dark underground and unreachable place what so many image board users yearned for this whole time?
